                        <interp inst="t18630511-698-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.—
<rs id="t18630511-698-punishment-38" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18630511-698-punishment-38" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
